alma.scheduling.planning_mode_sim.define
Class Priority

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--alma.scheduling.planning_mode_sim.define.Priority
public class Priority
extends java.lang.Object

The Priority class implements a priority that varies from 1 (lowest) to 10 (highest). The priorties have names:

  • HIGHEST (10)
  • HIGHER (9)
  • HIGH (8)
  • MEDIUMPLUS(7)
  • MEDIUM (6)
  • MEDIUMMINUS (5)
  • LOW (4)
  • LOWER (3)
  • LOWEST (2)
  • BACKGROUND (1)

Version:
1.00 Jun 4, 2003
Author:
Allen Farris
